dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents municipalities for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_Municipalities_2013.gdb. [The data serves as a reference for multiple uses. These uses include, but are not limited to; taxation, assessment, property locations, emergency response, regulation enforcement, and general mapping.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. For complete metadata documentation and most current online dataset download, please visit http://data-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
